\fs22\fsmilli11200 \cf4 \super [9]}}\'a0Nh\'e0 nghi\'ean c\uc0\u7913 u "S\u7903  gi\u7843 n" D\u432  Duy C\u432 \u417 ng \u7903  th\'e0nh ph\u7889 \'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng_Sa,_H%E1%BB%93_Nam"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng Sa}}, t\uc0\u7881 nh\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/H%E1%BB%93_Nam"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 H\uc0\u7891  Nam}}, Trung Qu\uc0\u7889 c cho r\u7857 ng: "Ng\u7885 c b\u7843 o An D\u432 \u417 ng n\'e0y l\'e0 c\u7911 a An D\u432 \u417 ng c\u7893  \u273 \u7841 i Vi\u7879 t Nam. An D\u432 \u417 ng h\'e0nh b\u7843 o c\'f3 l\u7895  \u273 eo, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 lo\u7841 i ng\u7885 c phi\u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i x\u432 a \u273 eo l\'e0m v\u7853 t b\'e1u h\u7897  th\'e2n, tr\u7915  t\'e0 \u273 \u7875  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c an l\'e0nh." Th\u7867  ng\u7885 c n\'e0y \u273 \'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u7903  ph\'eda \u273 \'f4ng nam v\'e0 c\'e1ch th\'e0nh ph\u7889 \'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Qu%E1%BA%A3ng_Ch%C3%A2u_(th%C3%A0nh_ph%E1%BB%91)"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 Qu\uc0\u7843 ng Ch\'e2u}}\'a018\'a0km, \uc0\u7903  tr\'ean h\u7841  l\u432 u s\'f4ng Vi\u7879 t Giang do m\u7897 t n\'f4ng d\'e2n khi cu\u7889 c \u273 \u7845 t \u273 \'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u7903  s\u432 \u7901 n n\'fai n\u259 m 1932. Nh\u7919 ng th\u7867  ng\u7885 c \u273 \'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u7903 \'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Qu%E1%BA%A3ng_Ch%C3%A2u_(th%C3%A0nh_ph%E1%BB%91)"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 Qu\uc0\u7843 ng Ch\'e2u}}\'a0kho\uc0\u7843 ng 200 th\u7867 , trong \u273 \'f3 c\'f3 th\u7867  ng\u7885 c kh\u7855 c ch\u7919  An D\u432 \u417 ng. Khi\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nam_Vi%E1%BB%87t"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 Nam Vi\uc0\u7879 t}}\'a0\uc0\u273 \'e1nh b\u7841 i\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%82u_L%E1%BA%A1c"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \'c2u L\uc0\u7841 c}}, c\'e1c b\'e1u v\uc0\u7853 t c\u7911 a\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%82u_L%E1%BA%A1c"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \'c2u L\uc0\u7841 c}}\'a0l\'e0 chi\uc0\u7871 n l\u7907 i ph\u7849 m n\'ean m\u7899 i \u273 \'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u7903 \'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Qu%E1%BA%A3ng_Ch%C3%A2u_(th%C3%A0nh_ph%E1%BB%91)"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 Qu\uc0\u7843 ng Ch\'e2u}}.{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/An_D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng_V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng#cite_note-10"}}{\fldrslt 
